  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/dee25ff8fba8ab1e5dd2eeeca7a76f94.poster.avif?t=1766664039\" width=582 height=131 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/dee25ff8fba8ab1e5dd2eeeca7a76f94.webm?t=1766664039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>UFO sightings have grown exponentially the last few months, and the Secret Service is spread too thin to devise convincing cover-ups for all of them. The solution? Enlist the help of Lucas Brazier; a former brass worker turned surface-to-air missile specialist. As the newest recruit in the fleet of AA-privateers, your job is to shoot down any and all UFOs spotted in the sky. <br><br>Will You Follow Orders?<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/c59a156f80160e46049a6cc4cad77e67.poster.avif?t=1766664039\" width=607 height=105 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/c59a156f80160e46049a6cc4cad77e67.webm?t=1766664039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Typing gameplay with multiple difficulties<br><br></li><li>Special missiles and equipment to buy<br><br></li><li>Two factions to help or destroy<br><br></li><li>Unlockable extras, including Boss Rush, Survival and Target Library<br><br></li><li><i>Aliens</i></li></ul></strong><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/83808d143fa656001613a34c136b12c0.poster.avif?t=1766664039\" width=600 height=157 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/83808d143fa656001613a34c136b12c0.webm?t=1766664039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Missile Input features the musical work of Nicolas.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Halfway Home<br></li><li>East of Eden<br></li><li>I don't want to live in a world without you<br></li><li>Hope<br></li><li>Archon Ladabaoth<br></li><li>Pure Pleroma<br></li><li>Basilides Lost Exegetica</li></ul></strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/dee25ff8fba8ab1e5dd2eeeca7a76f94.poster.avif?t=1766664039\" width=582 height=131 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/dee25ff8fba8ab1e5dd2eeeca7a76f94.webm?t=1766664039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>UFO sightings have grown exponentially the last few months, and the Secret Service is spread too thin to devise convincing cover-ups for all of them. The solution? Enlist the help of Lucas Brazier; a former brass worker turned surface-to-air missile specialist. As the newest recruit in the fleet of AA-privateers, your job is to shoot down any and all UFOs spotted in the sky. <br><br>Will You Follow Orders?<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/c59a156f80160e46049a6cc4cad77e67.poster.avif?t=1766664039\" width=607 height=105 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/c59a156f80160e46049a6cc4cad77e67.webm?t=1766664039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Typing gameplay with multiple difficulties<br><br></li><li>Special missiles and equipment to buy<br><br></li><li>Two factions to help or destroy<br><br></li><li>Unlockable extras, including Boss Rush, Survival and Target Library<br><br></li><li><i>Aliens</i></li></ul></strong><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871450/extras/83808d143fa656001613a34c136b12c0.poster.avif?t=1766664039